               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18370130-name-567" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18370130-name-567" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370130-name-567" type="surname" value="HEMPSTEAD"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18370130-name-567" type="given" value="HENRY WILLIAM"></interp>HENRY WILLIAM HEMPSTEAD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am shopman to Thomas Nicholls, of Gray's Inn-lane, a pawnbroker. I missed this pair of trowsers from the shop counter on the morning of the 17th of January—the prisoner had been employed about the premises to fetch errands.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18370130-name-568" type="witnessName">
