                  </hi>. I am shopman to Mr. clunes, of Liquorpond-street.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183701300096"></xptr>
               <p>On Tuesday, the 17th of January, the prisoner brought these trowsers to pledge—he put them on the counter, but did not say any thing—I saw a ticket on the top, and on finding that, I sent to Mr. Nicholls.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
