                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable G</hi> 117.) I took the prisoner into custody.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I throw myself on the mercy of the Court—I came from Sebastian in Spain, and received an injury there, which renders me wholly incapable of doing hard jobs.</p>
